{"word":"G3333 - μετακαλέω - metakaléō - met-ak-al-eh'-o - Call","slug":"G3333","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μετακαλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>metakaléō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>met-ak-al-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Call"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>μετακαλέω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>metakaleo</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>met-ak-al-eh'-o</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to call from one place to another, to summon </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to call one's self </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G3326\">G3326</a> and <a href=\"#/G2564\">G2564</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 11:16,4 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G3326\">G3326</a> and <a href=\"#/G2564\">G2564</a>; to <i>call elsewhere</i> that is <b><i>summon</i></b>: - call (for hither). "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1458\">G1458</a>, <a href=\"#/G1462\">G1462</a>, <a href=\"#/G1528\">G1528</a>, <a href=\"#/G1577\">G1577</a>, <a href=\"#/G1941\">G1941</a>, <a href=\"#/G2564\">G2564</a>, <a href=\"#/G2821\">G2821</a>, <a href=\"#/G2822\">G2822</a>, <a href=\"#/G4292\">G4292</a>, <a href=\"#/G4341\">G4341</a>, <a href=\"#/G4779\">G4779</a>, <a href=\"#/G479\">G479</a>"}]}